            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Core ($16.50/month billed annually) gives you unlimited downloads of 28M+ assets plus 10 AI generations per month. Plus ($39/month) adds 100 AI generations monthly. Ultimate ($109/month) is built for power users and teams who need the full suite of AI tools and maximum generation capacity.",
