            "text": "Absolutely. At $16.50 per month with unlimited downloads and lifetime commercial licensing, it's one of the best value propositions in creative tools. A single stock video clip or template on other platforms often costs more than an entire month of Envato Elements. If you produce even 5-10 assets per month, the subscription pays for itself immediately.",
